data.description: Check out this beautiful 3 bedroom OPEN floorplan home sitting on 5 private acres with FIREFLY fiber optic internet. Located just 15 mins from the town of Appomattox this home sits well off the road with woods on all sides and has a nice deck/patio area around back. The home has a super OPEN layout with 2 living areas a large kitchen and 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The kitchen has ample storage and countertop space, a large eat at island and black stainless steel appliances. The main bedroom has a nice walk in closet and main bathroom with a standup shower, double sink and a garden tub. Utility area has more storage along with a washer & dryer that convey. CVEC electric & firefly internet. Call today to take a look.
